<p>Bikini weather: Munn looked slender in the skimpy triangle top that had spaghetti straps. Her long dark hair was worn down and she had on a dark cap</p>

<p>And the Predator star's suspicions were further fueled by the fact her partner only liked to have sex in the dark and 'spooning from behind' so he didn't see her face.</p>

