<p>Olivia - who previously dated footballer Aaron Rodgers for three years until 2017 and recently split from Tucker Roberts after a year of dating - admitted she's faked enjoyment with more than one partner in the past and it's something she regrets.</p>

<p>She said: 'I swear to god I'm like I regret every time I have fake moaned because these guys are out there feeling so f****** confident.'      </p>

